cs.IT, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.NA, cs.SI

The paper discusses algorithms related to signal processing and optimization, which are commonly found in the sub-categories of Information Theory (cs.IT), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), Numerical Analysis (cs.NA), and Social and Information Networks (cs.SI). However, since the paper focuses on the comparison of two algorithms for sparse signal recovery, cs.IT and cs.LG are the most likely sub-categories.
